      "writtenOn": "2019-11-30T21:27:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If both projects use opencensus library, there\u0027ll be two spans: \"Send.HTTP:\u003cURL\u003e\" (uploaded from the calling project), and nested \"Recv.HTTP:\u003cURL\u003e\" (uploading from the project being called). But I don\u0027t really know how it would look. Docs aren\u0027t great. I don\u0027t know how visually different are \"a span linked to a parent span via AddLink\" and \"a span created as a child of a parent span\".",
